description.narrative:
2019 was a challenger year in terms of planning and monitoring. PM&E focused their efforts in two priorities during that year: i) strengthening and consolidate the programme monitoring mechanism, specifically the HPM, in the framework of the UNICEF Venezuela Humanitarian Response, and ii) strengthening of planning process to ensure aligning with CO Scale Up Plan, HRP and HAC.
The key results were: i) HPM mechanism was put in place and protocols and procedures were piloted. In 2020, one of priority to PM&E will be consolidate this mechanism; ii) AWP 2019 focused in humanitarian response alined with HRP and HAC. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/02/2020
